                        <p class="featured_text">Your Vegas Package features 3 nights hotel & casino stay at one of several Las Vegas locations. While each is unique, all of these resorts feature multiple dining and entertainment options. Regardless of which hotel & casino you end up staying at, you are sure to have a great experience during your Las Vegas getaway with us!</p>

                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Planet Hollywood</h2>
                            <p>
                                A modern hotel with all new contemporary rooms featuring modern furnishings and edgy artwork. Upscale dining options include Strip House Steakhouse and Koi, which is very well known for fine Japanese dining in New York and LA. If you are in the mood for something more casual, try Gordon Ramsay's Burger, Pinks Hot Dogs, Earl of Sandwich, PF Changs, or their famous "Spice Market" Buffet.
                                <br><br>
                                The PH also is home to the Miracle Mile Shops Las Vegas. In addition to great shopping and dining options, this area hosts multiple theatres including the V and Saxe theatres. Here you will find an assortment of shows which you can see using your show tickets that are included in this package. PH is also famous for the Zappos Theater which plays host to many headliners, including Jennifer Lopez, Pitbull, Lionel Richie, Backstreet Boys and more. While headliners are never included in our packages, while at PH you will have an opportunity to see world class shows right at your' hotel.
                            </p>

