                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Flamingo</h2>
                            <p>
                                Located center strip adjacent to the Linq and the 550 foot tall High Roller and boasting comfortable new rooms, a tropical Wildlife Habitat and a 15 acre space, Caribbean-style water playground known as Go Pool, Flamingo Las Vegas puts you right in the middle of the action.
                                <br><br>
                                There is no need to leave the resort for meals or entertainment. Flamingo Las Vegas is the home to Donnie & Marie, America's Got Talent's Puff The Magic Dragon, X Burlesque and Legends in Concert. Their dining options include a fantastic buffet, Center Cut Steakhouse, a food court and 2 casual restaurant/bars world famous for tropical style fun, Margaritaville and Carlos & Charlies.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/flamingo_img/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/flamingo_img/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
