                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Bally's</h2>
                            <p>
                                A property that offers a blend of something old and something new. The rooms at Bally's are more spacious than most and feature large showers and/or bath tubs. The dining options here are endless and include the Sterling Buffet every weekend at BLT Steak. This buffet offers an opportunity to indulge in sturgeon caviar, oysters, lobster tails, and several things dipped in chocolate. Shows include the return of Mr. Las Vegas, Wayne Newton, The Bronx Wanderers, Paranormal, a Motown tribute called "Solid Gold", the X ROCKS topless revue, and more.
                                <br><br>
                                In front of Bally's you will discover the Grand Bazaar Shops, an open-air market that you will want to check out. Also, be sure to visit Bally's Avenue Shops in the corridor connecting you to the Race and Sports Book and the Monorail station.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
