                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Treasure Island</h2>
                            <p>
                                Treasure Island Las Vegas, also known as TI, is located in the heart of the Las Vegas strip. This property is home to Mystere by Cirque du Soleil, The Avengers S.T.A.T.I.O.N. exhibit, over a dozen dining options, and great shops. There is a fabulous outdoor heated resort pool offering cabanas and double chaise lounges. There is also a free tram connecting the property to the Mirage and a walkway connecting you to a wonderful and unique shopping experience, the Fashion Show Mall.

                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/treasure_img/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/treasure_img/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
