                        </div>

                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Sahara Las Vegas</h2>
                            <p>
                                The new Sahara is part of the SLS Hotels family. They are famous for style, luxury and service and is part of the SBE family, global leaders in hospitality, cuisine, design, residences and entertainment. Their Vegas Hotel is a sleek and seductive property offering over 1300 guest rooms, a massive casino floor, pool with cabanas, and a plethora of bars and sought after nightlife options.
                                <br><br>
                                Tempting your taste buds and senses, dining options include a Bazaar Meat by Jose Andres which has been rated among the very best steakhouses in America. SLS is also home to Katsuya, a Japanese fine dining experience for the American palette, and Cleo, a Mediterranean-inspired reinvention of Tinseltown glamour. For more casual dining consider Unami Burger, 800 Degrees Neapolitan Pizzeria, The Perq, or Northside Café & Chinese Kitchen.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/sahara/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/sahara/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
