                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>The Linq</h2>
                            <p>Located in the center of the world-famous Las Vegas Strip, The Linq offers a collection of very trendy rooms designed in a contemporary style with high tech features. The High Roller, which is the world's largest observation wheel, anchors the Promenade, a curated outdoor shopping and entertainment complex. You will find a carefully selected collection of shops, restaurants and bars as well as entertainment options here.</p>

