                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Rio Hotel &amp; Casino</h2>
                            <p>
                                The Rio is the only "all suite" property in our collection. We are talking about 50 sq. feet with contemporary décor and floor to ceiling windows. Although the
                                suites are super comfortable, the Rio is all about the resort experience to be found outside of your accommodations.
                                <br><br>
                                The Rio features 2 major attractions, the 50 story high Voodoo Zipline and Kiss by Monster Mini Golf. You will also find great dining options including Guy Fieri's Mexican joint, El Borra Borracho shows here including headliners Penn & Teller, WOW (World of Wonder), Chippendales and more.
                            </p>

