                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Luxor</h2>
                            <p>
                                This vibrant Egyptian Pyramid-themed casino resort on the south end of the Strip is housed in a 30-story pyramid topped with a 315,000-watt light beam. The dining and drinking options include a steak and seafood bar, a Mexican cantina, a pizza joint, and an Irish pub. You will also enjoy a bustling casino, fitness center and a salon, plus a spa and an outdoor pool.
                                <br><br>
                                Entertainment option includes some of the top shows in Vegas. Chris Angel's Mind Freak, Blue Man Group, Carrot Top and Fantasy. If you are into competitive gaming, Luxor is the home of E-Sports Arena Las Vegas.  Luxor is an MGM Resort, and as their guest you can take advantage of special deals like a 3 for $57 offer on attractions such as Shark Reef, Sigfried and Roy's Secret Garden and Dolphin Habitat, Bellagio Gallery of Fine Art, CSI the Experience, Big Apple Roller Coaster, Bodies…The Exhibition, Adventure Dome, and all day passes to 4-D movies at Excalibur.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/luxor_img/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/luxor_img/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
