                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>Excalibur</h2>
                            <p>
                                Located on the south end of the Strip, this Camelot-themed resort casino is one of few family friendly resorts in Sin City. Dining options are endless and include a food court, buffet, Camelot Steakhouse, Bucca Di Beppo, and Dicks Last Resort. You will find shows including the Tournament of Kings and the Australian Bee Gees, both of which are great for all ages, as well as Thunder from Down Under for the grown folks. They also host the Ultimate 4D Experience, where you can join some of your favorite characters in a 15 minute adventure. You can also check out the Fun Dungeon for some great arcade games.
                                <br><br>
                                The resort is also connected by tram to Mandalay Bay and Luxor and by walkway to MGM, New York New York, The Park and T-Mobile Arena. Excalibur is an MGM Resort, and as their guest you can take advantage of special deals like a 3 for $57 offer on attractions such as Shark Reef, Sigfried and Roy's Secret Garden and Dolphin Habitat, Bellagio Gallery of Fine Art, CSI the Experience, Big Apple Roller Coaster, Bodies…The Exhibition, Adventure Dome, and all day passes to 4-D movies at Excalibur.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/excaliber_img/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/excaliber_img/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
