                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="hotel_content_block">
                            <h2>The D Downtown</h2>
                            <p>
                                Long on fun and short on ordinary, The D is  is located on the Fremont Street Experience. A fun property with nice rooms with a  modern décor, fun bars with flare bartenders, and several shows plus free music nightly on 3 Fremont stages including one immediately outside of the hotel. For a casual meal, try American Coney Island, a well-known Detroit favorite for almost a century among locals and visitors. If you are in the mood for fine dining, Andiamo Steakhouse, boasting American prime and Italian flavor.
                                <br><br>
                                The D's showroom has anywhere from 1-4 different shows every day/evening. Marriage Can Be Murder has been running for nearly 20 years now, the longest running dinner show in Vegas. Defending the Caveman is another popular show that has been running for many years now. The D also has a couple of comedy offerings to choose from.
                            </p>

                            <div class="gallary_img_block">
                                <a class="group2" href="~/images/hotel_img/downtown_img/1.jpg" title=""><img src="~/images/hotel_img/downtown_img/1.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" /></a>
